## A Legacy of Transformation: The urbanclay Journey
Our story is rooted in a deep appreciation for natural materials and the art of sustainable construction. Urbanclay was founded with the ambition to revolutionize the way we build, aiming to make a lasting impact on both the spaces we create and the world we live in.
What started as a modest initiative in Mumbai has blossomed into a nationwide presence. Today, Urbanclay proudly serves clients across all major cities in India, including Bangalore, Hyderabad, Delhi, Maharashtra, Kerala, Uttar Pradesh, Bihar, Gujarat, Telangana, and more. We’ve completed over 700 projects, collaborating with top architects and interior designers to deliver excellence in every corner of the country.
Our commitment extends beyond construction; it’s about making a difference. For every product purchased, we plant 10 trees, embodying our dedication to environmental stewardship and sustainability. This initiative reflects our belief in giving back to the environment and supporting a greener future.
Urbanclay is more than a company—it’s a legacy of transforming spaces and empowering lives. We offer a diverse range of products, from terracotta cladding to hollow clay blocks, all crafted from 100% natural clay. Our products are designed not only for their beauty and durability but also for their positive impact on energy efficiency and environmental sustainability.
Recognizing that every project is unique, we also specialize in custom clay product manufacturing. We understand that each project may require a different approach, and our team is dedicated to delivering tailored solutions to meet specific needs.
Our materials have been a cornerstone in prestigious projects across India, including collaborations with leading architects and designers. In every major superdry project, our products are the material of choice, underscoring our commitment to quality and excellence.
We invite you to be part of this journey of transformation. Explore our sustainable building solutions and discover how Urbanclay can help you create stunning, eco-friendly spaces. Together, let’s build not just structures, but a legacy of positive change and empowerment.

